{
  "stem": "11801.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, and there were no shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Wooden shoes were plentiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I think somebody must have made them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And on an aside, you know, now we go to Holland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we admire the wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we buy them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They're very uncomfortable, especially when you don't have socks to put in them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was no-- there was-- the clothing was a problem, although we always had something to wear.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But shoes, we didn't have.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But that's an aside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you know, the, all the German occupied buildings, houses, whatnot, were immediately raided.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everything was stolen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you know, I applauded it, personally, although a lot of people, you know, frowned on that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it was a very Catholic society with, you know, very strict rules.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was a tremendous-- for me-- a tremendous feeling of liberation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how, how long did that celebration go on?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- well, we only-- we were, you know, that, that was the only time we were allowed to go out to that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, as I said, I don't think they could have stopped us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We stayed for a few hours, I think.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, after liberation, I stayed until May of-- March of '46.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I had-- I didn't know, of course, if my mother was alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know what would happen to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, I, I did go back to school as soon as the war was over, which was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I had now-- I was now three years behind my contemporaries.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had lost the one year when I moved from Germany to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I lost two years when I didn't go to school at all in Belgium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was now three years behind.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
